d7148214-2fd8-41a8-9f0a-c4eb9782a860.title: Cook
d7148214-2fd8-41a8-9f0a-c4eb9782a860.text: What do you want? I'm busy!

options.text: Can you sell me any food?
Can you give me any free food?
I don't want anything from this horrible kitchen.

1fc103f4-88f3-4c8d-869c-d6696a32f969.title: <player>
1fc103f4-88f3-4c8d-869c-d6696a32f969.text: I don't want anything from this horrible kitchen.

0e2a1cd6-a1ee-4201-8bf6-6cbfe850a040.title: Cook
0e2a1cd6-a1ee-4201-8bf6-6cbfe850a040.text:
How dare you? I put a lot of effort into cleaning this
kitchen. My daily sweat and elbow-grease keep this
kitchen clean!

65954cd1-f222-45ed-a169-c44534e8f1e1.title: <player>
65954cd1-f222-45ed-a169-c44534e8f1e1.text: Can you give me any free food?

e9803b2e-acc4-476e-add2-cb4505569af3.title: Cook
e9803b2e-acc4-476e-add2-cb4505569af3.text: Can you give me any free money?

3f0bc515-f04e-4a2d-908b-aaa2684892ef.title: <player>
3f0bc515-f04e-4a2d-908b-aaa2684892ef.text: Why should I give you free money?

c851ef01-ffb8-4b7c-8a04-32d263d1f533.title: Cook
c851ef01-ffb8-4b7c-8a04-32d263d1f533.text: Why should I give you free food?

465861d5-c151-4746-bcbe-dd92f6a8c24d.title: <player>
465861d5-c151-4746-bcbe-dd92f6a8c24d.text: Can you sell me any food?

d23a2e56-c40d-4a78-8048-9a21a6766834.title: Cook
d23a2e56-c40d-4a78-8048-9a21a6766834.text:
I suppose I could sell you some cabbage, if you're
willing to pay for it. Cabbage is good for you.

f9650e50-5daf-40bf-abd4-29f5d2cb8ae7.title: What would you like to say?

options.text: No thanks, I don't like cabbage.

1cee9643-af7f-4a1e-8e67-8d1502a9a2e5.title: <player>
1cee9643-af7f-4a1e-8e67-8d1502a9a2e5.text: No thanks, I don't like cabbage.

9c511994-07be-4987-bd66-88392171574b.title: Cook
9c511994-07be-4987-bd66-88392171574b.text: Bah! People these days only appreciate junk food.

fe539347-1966-4735-8dcb-f501e10fe50c.title: Cook
fe539347-1966-4735-8dcb-f501e10fe50c.text:
It's a deal. Now, make sure you eat it all up. Cabbage
is good for you.

6dface5f-0c7d-4bb5-b2db-fc7785224c26.title: <player>
6dface5f-0c7d-4bb5-b2db-fc7785224c26.text: Oh dear. I don't seem to have enough money.
